explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the association between the electronic Medication Regimen Complexity Index (MRCI) at admission and complications during hospitalization using a multilevel logistic regression model. It does not mention or involve any machine learning techniques, algorithms, or models such as supervised learning, unsupervised learning, neural networks, or any other related keywords listed. The study is purely based on statistical analysis and does not utilize any advanced machine learning or deep learning methods.
